<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>SkillBridge</title>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <h1>Welcome to SkillBridge</h1>
  <p>Learn a new skill, or teach one you already know.</p>

  <div>
    <a href="/login"><button>Login</button></a>
    <a href="/register"><button>Register</button></a>
  </div>

  <h2>What is SkillBridge?</h2>
  <p>
    SkillBridge connects learners with instructors for peer-to-peer skill sharing.
    Search for a skill you want to learn, book a lesson, and leave a review once you're done.
  </p>

  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Register as a Learner or Instructor</li>
    <li>Search or browse skill listings</li>
    <li>Book a lesson with an instructor</li>
    <li>Leave a review and save your favourites</li>
  </ul>

</body>
</html>
